measurements.name: AVG_SNT_SCORE
measurements.description:
Weighted average of positive mentions, neutral mentions and negative mentions with weights 100, 50 and 0 respectively.
This metric ranges from 0 to 100 where a score closer to 100 represents positive sentiment and a score closer to 0 represents negative sentiment.
Calculation Logic: (100 * Positive Mentions + 50 * Neutral Mentions + 0 * Negative Mentions ) / ( Positive Mentions + Neutral Mentions + Negative Mentions)
